data.description: Check out this adorable single-story ranch-style home with an over-sized lot and pool in Round Rock. Lovely 3 Bed, 2 Bath, 1,946 sqft. home on a half-acre lot with easy access to local employers (Dell, Kalahari, Ascension Seton) and many amenities (HEB Plus, Living Spaces, Stone Hill Town Center, etc.). New Roof in 2021, new HVAC, water heater, flooring, paint and bathroom remodels in 2020. Don’t miss it! Buyer to verify utilities and square footage.
